cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.DL 

This paper is about developing a framework for linguistic annotation, which is a core area of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the development of language resources, which involves machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as well as natural language processing (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the harmonization of existing resources, which involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and potentially deep learning (cs.DL) techniques.
